728008f-a.text:
Springfield Boulevard (Rocky Hill Road), east side, north of the Long Island Motor Parkway about 700 feet, showing buildings on the property of the Valentine family from 1860-1891. S. Petrocosky was the owner in 1909. This is a set of two views.
January 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

728009f-a.text:
Springfield Boulevard (Rocky Hill Road), east side, north of the Long Island Motor Parkway about 700 feet, showing the home of Jeremiah Valentine in 1873. S. Petrowsky was the owner in 1909. The house was still standing in 1928.

January 1923.
